@*
    [TR] Bu dosya ne işe yarar: Genel karşılama (landing) sayfası — proje tanıtımı, özellik kartları, iş akışı özeti, kapsam dışı notu.
    [TR] Neden gerekli: Savunmada sistemin güncel kapsamını tek ekranda özetler; anonim ziyaretçiye CTA, oturum açmış kullanıcıya pano/yükleme yönlendirmesi sunar.
    [TR] İlgili: HomeController.Index, _Layout.cshtml, site.css (.home-*), Dashboard/Documents/Admin modülleri

    MODIFICATION NOTES (TR)
    - Modern landing düzeni: hero glow, güven rozetleri, adım zaman çizelgesi, ikonlu özellik ızgarası.
    - "How it works" workspace rehberi ile aynı 5 adım + Help hatırlatması.
    - Oturum durumuna göre CTA: Dashboard / Upload PDF veya Login / Register.
    - Mimari akış ve "future work" kutusu landing'den kaldırıldı (daha sade ana sayfa); detay FAQ'da kalabilir.
    - OCR yalnızca PDF içi seçili bölge; genel görüntü OCR kapsam dışı.
    - Zorluk: Kolay.
*@
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home";
    var isSignedIn = User.Identity?.IsAuthenticated ?? false;
}

<div class="home-landing">
    <section class="home-hero text-white position-relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="home-hero__glow home-hero__glow--one" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="home-hero__glow home-hero__glow--two" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="container position-relative py-5 py-lg-6">
            <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <span class="home-eyebrow">Graduation Project · CreativeDoc</span>
                    <h1 class="home-hero__title display-5 fw-bold mb-3">
                        Translate, analyze, and visualize PDF content — one workspace.
                    </h1>
                    <p class="home-hero__lead mb-4">
                        Select any region on your document, extract text or capture an image, then run AI tools from a built-in chat panel. Simple steps, clear results.
                    </p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
                        @if (isSignedIn)
                        {
                            <a class="btn btn-accent btn-lg px-4 shadow-sm" asp-controller="Dashboard" asp-action="Index">Open Dashboard</a>
                            <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-4" asp-controller="Documents" asp-action="Upload">Upload PDF</a>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <a class="btn btn-accent btn-lg px-4 shadow-sm" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">Get started free</a>
                            <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-4" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Login">Sign in</a>
                        }
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 home-trust-pills">
                        <span class="home-trust-pill">📄 PDF-first workflow</span>
                        <span class="home-trust-pill">🔤 Region OCR only</span>
                        <span class="home-trust-pill">💬 AI chat workspace</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5">
                    <div class="home-hero-panel rounded-4 p-4 p-lg-5">
                        <p class="home-hero-panel__label mb-2">At a glance</p>
                        <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">Everything in one place</h2>
                        <ul class="home-checklist list-unstyled mb-0">
                            <li><span class="home-checklist__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Page viewer with drag-to-select regions</li>
                            <li><span class="home-checklist__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Paddle or Tesseract OCR on your selection</li>
                            <li><span class="home-checklist__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Image capture for multimodal AI tasks</li>
                            <li><span class="home-checklist__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Functions menu: Translate, Summarize, Visualize, Narrate…</li>
                            <li><span class="home-checklist__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Notebook history &amp; detailed result pages</li>
                            <li><span class="home-checklist__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Built-in guide + <strong>Help (?)</strong> anytime</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container home-body py-5">
        <section class="home-section mb-5 pb-2">
            <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-5">
                    <span class="home-eyebrow home-eyebrow--dark">Why CreativeDoc</span>
                    <h2 class="home-section__title h2 fw-bold mb-3">Focus on what matters in your PDF</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                        Instead of processing entire files, you choose the exact paragraph, figure, or table you care about.
                        Edit OCR text, pick an AI function, and keep every result in chat and your notebook.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <div class="row g-3">
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="home-stat-tile">
                                <span class="home-stat-tile__emoji" aria-hidden="true">🎯</span>
                                <strong>Precise selection</strong>
                                <span class="small text-muted">Normalized coordinates, zoom-aware</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="home-stat-tile">
                                <span class="home-stat-tile__emoji" aria-hidden="true">⚡</span>
                                <strong>Fast AI loop</strong>
                                <span class="small text-muted">Select → Run → chat result</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="home-stat-tile">
                                <span class="home-stat-tile__emoji" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</span>
                                <strong>Admin ready</strong>
                                <span class="small text-muted">Moderation &amp; audit tools</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="home-stat-tile">
                                <span class="home-stat-tile__emoji" aria-hidden="true">🔌</span>
                                <strong>Swappable providers</strong>
                                <span class="small text-muted">Gemini, Hugging Face, mock</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="home-section mb-5">
            <div class="text-center mb-4 mb-lg-5">
                <span class="home-eyebrow home-eyebrow--dark">How it works</span>
                <h2 class="home-section__title h2 fw-bold mb-2">Five steps to your first result</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0 mx-auto home-section__subtitle">Same flow as the in-app workspace guide — easy to follow even if you're new.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="home-steps">
                <article class="home-step">
                    <div class="home-step__num">1</div>
                    <div class="home-step__body">
                        <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">Select a region</h3>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Drag on the PDF to highlight the area you want.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="home-step">
                    <div class="home-step__num">2</div>
                    <div class="home-step__body">
                        <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">Text or image</h3>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Extract with OCR or capture the selection as an image.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="home-step">
                    <div class="home-step__num">3</div>
                    <div class="home-step__body">
                        <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">Edit if needed</h3>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Fix OCR text in the panel before sending to AI.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="home-step home-step--highlight">
                    <div class="home-step__num">4</div>
                    <div class="home-step__body">
                        <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">Pick a function</h3>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Translate, Summarize, Explain, Visualize, Math, Narrate…</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="home-step home-step--highlight">
                    <div class="home-step__num">5</div>
                    <div class="home-step__body">
                        <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">Run &amp; review</h3>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Choose options, press Run — see output in chat.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="home-step home-step--help">
                    <div class="home-step__num home-step__num--muted">?</div>
                    <div class="home-step__body">
                        <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">Need help later?</h3>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Tap <strong>Help</strong> under the Functions column anytime.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="home-section mb-5">
            <div class="text-center mb-4 mb-lg-5">
                <span class="home-eyebrow home-eyebrow--dark">Features</span>
                <h2 class="home-section__title h2 fw-bold mb-2">Built for real document workflows</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="row g-4">
                @{
                    var features = new (string Icon, string Title, string Text)[]
                    {
                        ("📑", "PDF Workspace", "Upload, preview pages, zoom, and select regions with live toolbar metrics."),
                        ("🔤", "Region OCR", "OCR on the selected area only — Paddle or Tesseract from the popup menu."),
                        ("💬", "AI Chat", "Per-document chat history with operation chips and voice messages."),
                        ("🖼️", "Multimodal", "Send cropped images to Explain, Visualize, and vision-capable models."),
                        ("🔊", "Narration", "Gemini TTS turns text into audio saved in chat and notebook."),
                        ("📓", "Notebook", "Searchable saved outputs with full parameter details."),
                        ("❓", "Smart guide", "First-document onboarding modal; reopen from Help on Functions."),
                        ("🛡️", "Moderation", "Admin tools for users, documents, chat, and AI results."),
                        ("⚙️", "Extensible", "Provider layer swap via configuration — no UI rewrite."),
                    };
                }
                @foreach (var f in features)
                {
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                        <div class="home-feature-card h-100">
                            <span class="home-feature-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">@f.Icon</span>
                            <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-2">@f.Title</h3>
                            <p class="small text-muted mb-0">@f.Text</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                }
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="home-cta rounded-4 text-center p-4 p-lg-5 mb-2">
            <h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-2">Ready to try it?</h2>
            @if (isSignedIn)
            {
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">Upload a PDF and open the workspace — the guide will walk you through step one.</p>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center gap-2">
                    <a class="btn btn-accent btn-lg px-4" asp-controller="Documents" asp-action="Upload">Upload PDF</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4" asp-controller="Dashboard" asp-action="Index">Dashboard</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-link link-app btn-lg" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Faq">Read FAQ</a>
                </div>
            }
            else
            {
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">Create a free account, upload a document, and follow the built-in guide on your first workspace.</p>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center gap-2">
                    <a class="btn btn-accent btn-lg px-4" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">Create account</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Login">Sign in</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-link link-app btn-lg" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Faq">Read FAQ</a>
                </div>
            }
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
